2:T437,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"Article","headline":"The True Cost of Electric Driveway Gates in London (2026 Guide)","description":"Wondering how much electric driveway gates cost in London? Read our 2026 pricing guide covering materials, automation kits, and running costs.","url":"https://www.drivewaygateslondon.co.uk/guides/electric-driveway-gates-cost-london/","datePublished":"2026-01-10","dateModified":"2026-01-10","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://www.drivewaygateslondon.co.uk/images/gates/gate-aluminium-sliding-modern-dark-brick.png","width":1200,"height":630},"author":{"@type":"Organization","name":"Driveway Gates London","url":"https://www.drivewaygateslondon.co.uk"},"publisher":{"@type":"Organization","name":"Driveway Gates London","url":"https://www.drivewaygateslondon.co.uk","logo":{"@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://www.drivewaygateslondon.co.uk/android-chrome-512x512.png","width":512,"height":512}},"mainEntityOfPage":{"@type":"WebPage","@id":"https://www.drivewaygateslondon.co.uk/guides/electric-driveway-gates-cost-london/"}}3:T6de,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"How much do electric driveway gates cost in London on average?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"A fully automated driveway gate installation in London typically costs between £4,500 and £10,000 for a standard residential property. Budget projects using softwood gates and surface-mounted motors can come in below £4,000, while premium bespoke installations with wrought iron, underground motors, and full access control can exceed £20,000."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Are aluminium gates cheaper than wooden gates in London?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On initial supply cost, aluminium and good-quality hardwood gates are broadly comparable. However, aluminium gates have a significantly lower lifetime cost because they require no annual treatment, oiling, or repainting. Over a 10-year period, the maintenance cost of hardwood gates in London can add several hundred pounds per year."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Do I need planning permission for electric gates in London?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Gates under 1 metre tall adjacent to a highway, or under 2 metres elsewhere, are generally permitted development. However, London has a high concentration of conservation areas and Article 4 directions that override this. Always check with your local planning authority before installation."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How long does an electric gate installation take in London?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"A standard residential electric gate installation takes 2 to 4 days from start to finish. Complex sites, bespoke gates, or properties requiring planning consent will take longer."}}]}6:["slug","electric-driveway-gates-cost-london","d"]
